snippet.title: The Designer’s Curse Gameplay Trailer 1
snippet.description:
My biggest horror project yet.

Chapter One Releases Late June- Early July
Featuring Original Soundtrack composed by Mikko Tarmia (Composer of Amnesia: The dark descent and Soma, and other Frictional Games' games)
3D Enemy Modeling by Colby Ryan Williams. 
Art concepts by Ruby Kennedy.
